title: Fuzion Frenzy soundtrack
description:
128kbps VBR AAC rips from the game options menu, and in-game rips from the three DJ-ing minigames (with sound effects disabled, obviously). Some tracks sound like they stop abruptly, but that is how they were created for the game - with looping in mind. I&#039;ve cut as close to those stops as possible, so tracks are optimized for looping or crossfades.

My connection is not heroic, so please be patient with initial seeding!
